properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 5 at 3:38AM EST until February 5 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt
expected. Seas near 5 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 PM EST THIS EVENING
